POE/Component/Daemon version 0.1001
=================================


This component attempts to make building daemons in POE as easy as possible.
It implements pre-forking, post-forking and non-forking daemons.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

    POE
    POE::API::Peek

